Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然见到了「艾利尊战役」\N当时罗曼洛夫的部下罗博特上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所见 基本不开口说话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 他无法出任证人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之画…火的战场…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 多亏公安的通行证
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此简单就能见面的理由就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他明天移送到你那之前 会把他在HESNER公司工作时的资料给你传过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象白费工夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是从她没受到妨碍 平安无事这一点上能得出点结论
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人有没有留下任何证据的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者罗曼洛夫体制并非如此团结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:08.79,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:08.79,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:10.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:10.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上机车 马力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}试着去感受心的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞跃吧！尽你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸腾有如泉涌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:24.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:24.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我们的周遭布满陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用泪水洗去血染的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:31.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:31.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让双眼避开所有的蛊惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之风会引领我们向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:55.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:55.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波涛汹涌的世界里找寻指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:59.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:59.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背骑的身影穿梭其间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们需要的是你们的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去创造属于我们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:17.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
